  "slug": "spacefrogs-hungry-hungry-frogs-froggycraft-addon",
  "title": "SpaceFrog's Hungry Hungry Frogs *FroggyCraft Addon*",
  "description": "Adds FroggyCraft-specific hostile mobs to the frog food list of SpaceFrog's Hungry Hungry Frogs (can be used with any modded mods found in the FroggyCraft modpack)",
  "body": "In addition to adding all vanilla hostile mobs, this datapack adds hostile mobs from the FroggyCraft modpack to the frog food list of ([**_SpaceFrog's Hungry Hungry Frogs_**](https://modrinth.com/datapack/spacefrogs-hungry-hungry-frogs)) datapack. If you're running some or all of the mods from FroggyCraft that add custom hostile mobs, this datapack will expand the types of mobs frogs can eat. However, if you run this datapack without the base SpaceFrog's Hungry Hungry Frogs datapack, your frogs will be left pretty underpowered, and no one wants to see a frog exploded by a creeper! The base datapack adds buffs to frogs to make sure your froggy friends stand a good chance in any fight they get into.\n\nThis datapack is also a good option for those running vanilla Minecraft who want to give all frogs the ability to attack hostile vanilla mobs without the getting the buffs found in SpaceFrog's Hungry Hungry Frogs.\n",
